item.title: ![CDATA[Reggae Mix 1 Worlds Best OLDSKOOL Reggae MIXTAPE STEVE NSC]]
item.description:
![CDATA[Thanks all for all your support much appreciated 🙏🏽🙏🏿🙏🏾🙏🏼🙏
Please click *****SUBSCRIBE***** for the latest new mixes to the channel. Please see other mixes I’ve uploaded.
Mix 1 is a Selection of a few great Reggae tracks I've loved over the years, mostly old skool but some new skool that have the same old MIXTAPE vibe, mixed live on decks not pieced together on a computer so will have old mixtape original sound with imperfections. Many Memories from Coventry's West indian club back in the 80's. Have tried to make this like old skool mix mashed together, not like a clean super slick beat matched perfect mix of todays standard. Hey back then we often just recorded on tape to tape, just pausing the recorded tape in between tracks, then blasted from a ghetto blaster so no real mixing as such but sounded great:) the tracks are mixed different from the original tracks, length, bmp, tone, echo etc...so please goto the relevant music download sites to find the original.
RIP my ol]]
